  "schema_version": 1.4,
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Crowded Veil",
      "sections": [
        {
          "image": {
            "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png",
            "name": "Additional Lore",
            "type": "image"
          },
          "name": "The Many Are One",
          "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
          "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
          "sources": [
            {
              "link": {
                "alt": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight pg. 80",
                "aonid": 255,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight pg. 80",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight",
              "page": 80,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "subtype": "sidebar",
          "text": "A colony of crowded veil hosts appears unlinked to a casual observer. As intelligent, moving fungi, they can stray far from their clonal siblings, yet cannot move beyond regions that support their growth. On Golarion, this limits the crowded veil to Tanglebriar alone.",
          "type": "section"
        }
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight pg. 80",
            "aonid": 255,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight pg. 80",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight",
          "page": 80,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Only one crowded veil exists, but it does so as separate entities in many different bodies. As each \u201cindividual\u201d member shares a core extraplanar essence with the others, communication between them moves without regard to planar boundaries or the limitations of distance, allowing for swift transmission of information throughout Tanglebriar and beyond.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
    {
      "link": {
        "alt": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight pg. 80",
        "aonid": 255,
        "game-obj": "Sources",
        "name": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight pg. 80",
        "type": "link"
      },
      "name": "Pathfinder #212: A Voice in the Blight",
      "page": 80,
      "type": "source"
    }
  ],
